{"tid":218971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湖北男散步被狗撞跌　致10級傷殘獲賠12萬","createTime":"2017-04-27T01:23:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T08:34:11.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a267191097b1d3db7bf4fb056c6074f8a724774d","tid":218971,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T01:23:44.000Z","msg":"湖北武漢一名段姓男子，去年散步時被一隻大狗從背後撞倒，造成十級傷殘。段男就此對狗主人起訴，直至昨日內地傳媒從當地法院獲悉，狗主人被判予賠償傷者段男12萬元（人民幣‧下同）。<br />\n<br />\n據相關報道指，傷者段男於去年5月某晚散步時，突然被一隻白色的金毛犬撞倒在地，隨後段男發現自己的腿無法動彈，被送醫救治後，經鑒定為傷殘十級，段男決定將狗主人胡某告上法庭。<br />\n<br />\n審訊中，狗主人胡某辯稱，原告段男當時亦帶了狗，但沒有使用牽引繩，其受傷與兩狗嬉鬧有關，是原告段男自身沒有注意到安全防護。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/dBTxrVR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FdBTxrVR.gif&h=2d3dae97&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3810e2d2525160e8d1c9c3fec53225599f2304a8","tid":218971,"uid":20305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T01:27:58.000Z","msg":"見到標題大笑左"},{"pid":"577e8b7df79f240b69995bb909e1a7d8f06c8bf7","tid":218971,"uid":35205,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T01:29:01.000Z","msg":"隨時係屎忽落地<br />\n尾龍骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6a7d7e1d7c341b13dcf8843d2e6d0b1399ad48","tid":218971,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T01:29:24.000Z","msg":"張圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f1bb99c9ab2a0043cce713cd0509c3c8340484","tid":218971,"uid":38757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T01:35:04.000Z","msg":"金毛尋回狗就有D軒強....<br />\n你話大丹個類都話姐...."},{"pid":"362eb22ba0948010f0f697b40b2707506639fdf4","tid":218971,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T01:38:42.000Z","msg":"十級傷殘既證明應該都係幾萬內，支那仔識玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/no